---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About" description="Myles Liu — frontend engineer, AI agent practitioner.">
  <section class="page-header">
    <h1 class="page-title" data-en="about" data-zh="关于">about</h1>
  </section>
  <div class="prose about-prose">
    <p data-en="Frontend engineer, working on monitoring infrastructure. Based in Shanghai."
       data-zh="前端工程师，专注监控基础设施方向，在上海。">
      Frontend engineer, working on monitoring infrastructure. Based in Shanghai.
    </p>
    <p data-en="On the side, I build tools around AI agents — ant-protocol (multi-agent governance), prism (personal profile engine), oasis-openclaw (social simulation with real agents), worldmind (world model engine), and temporal-crystal (living memory)."
       data-zh="业余时间，我在构建围绕 AI Agent 的工具 — ant-protocol（多 Agent 治理）、prism（个人画像引擎）、oasis-openclaw（社会模拟）、worldmind（世界模型引擎）和 temporal-crystal（活性记忆）。">
      On the side, I build tools around AI agents — <a href="https://github.com/mylesio/ant-protocol">ant-protocol</a> (multi-agent governance), <a href="https://github.com/mylesio/prism">prism</a> (personal profile engine), <a href="https://github.com/mylesio/oasis-openclaw">oasis-openclaw</a> (social simulation with real agents), <a href="https://github.com/mylesio/worldmind">worldmind</a> (world model engine), and <a href="https://github.com/mylesio/temporal-crystal">temporal-crystal</a> (living memory).
    </p>
    <p data-en="This site is my public knowledge base. Notes on things I'm learning, systems I'm building, ideas worth writing down. It's also designed to be readable by AI agents — clean HTML, llms.txt, every note at its own URL."
       data-zh="这个站点是我的公开知识库。记录我在学的东西、在做的系统、值得写下来的想法。同时也为 AI Agent 可读而设计 — 干净的 HTML、llms.txt、每篇笔记都有独立 URL。">
      This site is my public knowledge base. Notes on things I'm learning, systems I'm building, ideas worth writing down. It's also designed to be readable by AI agents — clean HTML, <a href="/llms.txt">llms.txt</a>, every note at its own URL.
    </p>
    <p data-en="These notes — conversations, code snippets, half-formed thoughts — are a record of how I think. Not a portfolio. Not a blog. Just evidence that something happened."
       data-zh="这些笔记 — 对话片段、代码摘录、半成型的想法 — 是我思考方式的记录。不是作品集，不是博客，只是留下曾经发生过什么的痕迹。">
      These notes — conversations, code snippets, half-formed thoughts — are a record of how I think. Not a portfolio. Not a blog. Just evidence that something happened.
    </p>

    <h2 data-en="links" data-zh="链接">links</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/mylesio">github.com/mylesio</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- ZH layer template for divider -->
  <template id="zh-content-tpl">
    <section class="page-header">
      <h1 class="page-title">关于</h1>
    </section>
    <div class="prose about-prose">
      <p>前端工程师，专注监控基础设施方向，在上海。</p>
      <p>业余时间，我在构建围绕 AI Agent 的工具 — <a href="https://github.com/mylesio/ant-protocol">ant-protocol</a>（多 Agent 治理）、<a href="https://github.com/mylesio/prism">prism</a>（个人画像引擎）、<a href="https://github.com/mylesio/oasis-openclaw">oasis-openclaw</a>（社会模拟）、<a href="https://github.com/mylesio/worldmind">worldmind</a>（世界模型引擎）和 <a href="https://github.com/mylesio/temporal-crystal">temporal-crystal</a>（活性记忆）。</p>
      <p>这个站点是我的公开知识库。记录我在学的东西、在做的系统、值得写下来的想法。同时也为 AI Agent 可读而设计 — 干净的 HTML、<a href="/llms.txt">llms.txt</a>、每篇笔记都有独立 URL。</p>
      <p>这些笔记 — 对话片段、代码摘录、半成型的想法 — 是我思考方式的记录。不是作品集，不是博客，只是留下曾经发生过什么的痕迹。</p>
      <h2>链接</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/mylesio">github.com/mylesio</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </template>
</Base>

<style>

  .about-prose { font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .about-prose p { margin-bottom: 1.35rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--text); }
  .about-prose a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: none; }
  .about-prose a:hover { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent); }
  .about-prose h2 {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin: 2.5rem 0 0.85rem;
  }
  .about-prose ul { list-style: none; }
  .about-prose li { padding: 0.35rem 0; font-size: 0.88rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
</style>
